title: #64 - Jacksfilms and Erik
description: On this extremely special episode of The H3 Podcast the boiz are back in the studio with us to discuss EVERYTHING. We talk about Jack's wedding, the Kanye controversy, Cosby's sentencing, detoxing from social media, watch lots of cringe videos... and have a phone interview with Kyle The Cougar Champ from our recent h3h3 video "This 31 Year Old Slam Dunks On A 91 Year Old Grandma".
